metadata.name: Introducing Cyrus #1/200
metadata.description: “Cyrus, a modern day archeologist, attempts to cross the barrier into an alternate reality where the past of Cesedria exists. He comes across a princess, whom he recognises from a vague memory during the turning point of his childhood, and fell in love with her. They had to find that a way to meet whilst traversing back and fourth between 2 parallel worlds, yet also the connection between both their families”
